# Crated       : 09 Apr 2022
# Updated      : 20 Jan 2025
# Comments     : Each ISO file must have its own checksum file.
#              : Checksum file must be one line only for ISO being checked.
#              : Checksum files must have one of the following extensions:
#              : .md5, .sha256, or .sha512
# TODO (Rick)  :
